<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">不负夏日，忙里偷闲。5月25日，经济管理学院在南区举办了一场歌会，二十余名经管学子参与此次活动，在活动中分享音乐，传递喜悦，用歌声充实假期，用歌声描绘青春。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717066932171078846.png" title="1717066932171078846.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717066945287043550.png" title="1717066945287043550.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717066956669054070.png" title="1717066956669054070.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717066966494091062.png" title="1717066966494091062.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717066977753070210.png" title="1717066977753070210.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717066999827064460.png" title="1717066999827064460.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在活动中，大家踊跃上台，一展歌喉，优美的歌声引起观众们发出整整欢呼，同时也吸引行人驻足观看，现场气氛十分融洽，加深了同学们之间的关系。</span><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717067033631003031.png" title="1717067033631003031.png" alt="image.png" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"/></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240530/1717067058819042443.png" title="1717067058819042443.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">此次歌会不仅丰富了同学们的假期生活，还增添了美好的青春回忆，相信这次活动会在时间的长河中如金子一样熠熠生辉，愿大家积极参与集体活动，尽情绽放青春之姿态！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"></span></p>